during the same week. 04,04,27,09,08 Program Station Rating 1. Home Improvement 
KABC 17.2 2. Roseanne KABC 15.8 3. 60 Minutes KCBS 13.9 4. Seinfeld KNBC 13.6 
5. Grace Under Fire KABC 13.3 6. Married ... With Children KTTV 13.1 7. "Jane's 
House" KCBS 12.9 8. Ellen KABC 12.7 9. 20/20 KABC 12.4 Murder, She Wrote KCBS 
12.4 Weekly Averages 
</P>
