<TEXT>
<P>
 Glendale City Councilman Larry Zarian will discuss safe neighborhoods during 
his monthly town hall meeting Thursday. 
</P>
<P>
 Joining Zarian will be Sgt. Rick Young and Mary Mijach, a community service 
