<P>
 A Korean Air Lines jetliner skidded, crashed and burst into flames after 
landing today, but all 160 people aboard were rescued, South Korean television 
reported. 
</P>
<P>
 The Airbus A-300 skidded into a safety barricade on a rain-slick runway on the 
southern resort island of Cheju, KBS television said. 
