<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA081094-0213 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 068637 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
August 10, 1994, Wednesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 6; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
